                      "fill": "$text-primary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "これまで vimscript で書いていた neovim の設定を全面的に lua へ移行した。この記事ではその動機と手順、移行後に感じたメリットについてまとめる。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "AvdS0",
                      "name": "bh2",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "gap": 8,
                      "alignItems": "center",
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "n3yLa",
                          "name": "bh2h",
                          "fill": "$accent",
                          "content": "##",
                          "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "owubZ",
                          "name": "bh2t",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "content": "移行の動機",
                          "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                          "fontSize": 20,
                          "fontWeight": "700"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "id": "fcGv3",
                      "name": "bp2",
                      "fill": "$text-primary",
                      "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "content": "vimscript は歴史的経緯から記法が独特で、他の言語に慣れた開発者にとっては読みづらい部分が多い。lua は neovim にネイティブ統合されており、パフォーマンスの面でも有利だ。",
                      "lineHeight": 1.8,
                      "fontFamily": "IBM Plex Mono",
                      "fontSize": 15,
                      "fontWeight": "normal"
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
                      "id": "a1VET",
                      "name": "code-block",
                      "width": "fill_container",
                      "fill": "$code-bg",
                      "stroke": {
                        "align": "inside",
                        "thickness": 1,
                        "fill": "$border"
                      },
                      "layout": "vertical",
                      "padding": 20,
                      "children": [
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "13fOk",
                          "name": "cLang",
                          "fill": "$text-tertiary",
                          "content": "-- init.lua",
                          "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                          "fontSize": 12,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "wEjr8",
                          "name": "cL1",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "content": "vim.g.mapleader = ' '",
                          "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "WQJ9W",
                          "name": "cL2",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "content": "vim.opt.number = true",
                          "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        },
                        {
                          "type": "text",
                          "id": "q0BJK",
                          "name": "cL3",
                          "fill": "$text-primary",
                          "content": "vim.opt.termguicolors = true",
                          "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
                          "fontSize": 13,
                          "fontWeight": "normal"
                        }
                      ]
                    },
                    {
                      "type": "frame",
